profile:
CARGO CABBIE™, a Top choice for Professional Movers in Toronto. We have been voted by you, the residents of Toronto, BlogTO, Houzz, ThreeBestRated and HomeStars as “Best moving company in Toronto” Nine years in a row.  We provide high quality, professional packing, moving and storage services and unsurpassed customer care and service.  All of our moving teams are non-smoking, physically fit and in-house trained to ensure that your move is completed quickly and safely. Whether your move or pack is large or small we always do it with a smile, at cost effective rates (no hidden fees).  

Our customers are very loyal to us, in fact, 80% of our business is based on repeat customers and customer referrals. At CARGO CABBIE we offer premium professional moving and packing services for all of your Toronto moving needs. We also offer a full line of moving and packing supplies to assist with your pack and move and also rent eco-friendly plastic bins. 

We would love to hear from you!  Call us today at (647) 478-5422 so we can show you the difference an owner operated business can make!  Our reliable and professional Toronto movers and packers are here to help!

We're lovers of design, fine art and antiques.

Would you trust the people who move the Archibald Prize artworks with your precious antiques and heirlooms? Great, because that's us! Simply tell us when the move will cause the least amount of disruption to your home, office, gallery, store or your space, and we'll be there!

Our Vans & moving trucks are NEW, clean & fully equipped.
specialities:
Welcome to CARGO CABBIE®!

Let us take you on a little tour of our special services!  Cargo Cabbie provides high quality professional moving and packing services for all sizes and types of residential and commercial moves.  We also have a full-range of moving and packing supplies at our Box Shop that we can deliver straight to your door.
We help with all sizes of moves from Eight-bedroom houses to single-item deliveries (Cargo Cabbie Express).  We also provide in-home moves and on-site loading / unloading, if you are only looking to stage or rearrange your home, or move your furniture out to a pod / truck in your driveway.  We can help!  We also provide professional packing services if you would like help packing and/or unpacking your home or office.  You have the option of purchasing cardboard boxes or renting our eco-friendly plastic bins, whether we do the packing or you do.  Our crews are also skilled at furniture assembly / disassembly, if you have one or a few items you would like help with.  Whatever your moving or packing needs, we can help!

Visit our Box Shop online  We offer all sizes of boxes, bubble wrap, white newsprint, dish and glass kits, shrink wrap, tape, tape dispensers, art/mirror boxes, TV boxes and more!  If you are local to us in the downtown core of Toronto we can deliver your order free of charge.  

We look forward to hearing from you!  We're here to help!

profile:
Since 1992, Miracle Movers Toronto has provided thousands of satisfied customers with customized, comprehensive moving services across the GTA and Canada. Whether you're one person moving into a bachelor apartment or a midsize company moving 100 employees into a new office, our experienced, enthusiastic staff is ready to help you out.

In addition to providing basic transportation services, we can visit your home or office before the big day to plan the most efficient move possible, create a floor plan of your new destination so that you know precisely where your items will go, and even help pack - or provide boxes, padding and plastic wrap if you'd rather do so yourself. With satellite offices across Canada and partners around the world, we can then accommodate moves of any distancccommodate moves of any distance to any destination, including the USA.

At Miracle Movers Toronto, we pride ourselves on providing outstanding customer service: more than 80% of our customers are from referrals! Call us for free advice and quotations today!

profile:
Welcome to Viktoria Professional Movers – a company where customer care and satisfaction are our top priorities. 
 
There's no doubt about it, moving can be stressful!   Choosing responsible and experienced movers is one of the ways to alleviate that stress. When choosing a moving & storage company price is important, however the level of service your moving company provides you with is even more important, and often times cheap moving companies can end up costing you a fortune! Unfortunately, our industry abounds with companies whose aim to book as many jobs as they can by whatever means necessary. Many "lowball" estimates quickly balloon with unexpected charges while hurried workers provide disappointing service. For many of these companies protecting your property and ensuring your satisfaction is last on their list of priorities.
 
At Viktoria Professional Movers it's not about the number of moves, it's about the number of customers we leave happy & satisfied. Moving doesn't have to be complicated. Let us walk you through the process and get you on the way to a stress-free move to your new home. The key to a successful move is organization and we are the experts.
 
Whether you require moving, packing, or self-storage, you will never be just another client to us. Ever.
 
PIANO MOVING | PACKING MATERIALS | PACKING SERVICES, MOVING BIN RENTAL | STORAGE | SELF-STORAGE | LONG-DISTANCE MOVES | MOVING SUPPLIES

profile:
The goal at GetMovers is to provide detail-oriented moving assistance that's tailored to the needs of each customer.

That is why all GetMovers employees from call centre assistants to drivers get special trainings and their salary is highly affected by our customers satisfaction.

Our quality management system is adapting quickly to client’s needs, saving you time and money.

So, if you want to move your belongings stress-free, on time and in full safety GetMovers is the company to turn to.

We are specializing on local residential and commercial moving. Moving can be very stressful and complicated if you haven’t chosen the right moving company and completed all the preparations needed, ahead of your moving day.
You should be checking if the company have full insurance coverage for your content and the properties, full equipment including packaging materials and tools to assemble and dissemble your furniture, how many years they are in business and read their third party reviews and must have back up trucks just in case something happen on your moving date! Our Team will be happy to advice you on other things that are extremely important during your move, so call us today and will be gladly assisting you.


Moving process starts with packing.

Packing is really time consuming.

Do you know that a 2-bedroom apartment will typically take a homeowner or renter 6 hours – 1 day to pack. A two-bedroom home will likely take up to 2 days

Our trained GetMovers team is happy to free you several precious hours.

We know how to handle bulky, fragile, oddly shaped and unique items to prevent damage while transportation.
We use high quality packing supplies, containers, wardrobe boxes to ensure the smoothness of moving process.

If you prefer packing by yourself, we can deliver all necessary packing materials to your doorstep.

We also provide Partial Packing Service. It means that we would pack or unpack only large items or pack up items in a specific room.

The decision is always yours.

Get in touch and we'll Pack and unpack It for You.



Getmovers has a large operating network across Canada. So, if you. need to relocate from Toronto to Vancouver or from Edmonton to Calgary we are happy to help you.

We’re not just moving experts, we’re relocation experts. Since 2008 we constantly enriching our expertise moving people and businesses around Canada.

We have the knowledge you need for a successful relocation.

We've partnered with competent international moving companies near you to help you ship your goods to any country in the world.

You can delegate us the whole process or the most time-consuming tasks while relocation.


Get your quote on get movers.ca


Looking for secure and climate control storage space with full access to? With over 10,000 Sqft   storage capacity GetMovers provides secure solutions for short or long-term storage.

Whether you need to store furniture, commercial goods or professional equipment, our secure storage facilities across Canada are equipped with the best technology to keep your belongings safe.

Our storage facilities are regularly inspected and well equipped, we make sure your belongings are securely stored in the best conditions.

Get Movers offers both private and corporate relocation services.

A well-designed action plan of your office relocation would minimize the loss of productivity for your business.

GetMovers are well trained to pack and move your company’s assets such as office furniture and electronics to your new premises.

You probably would ask yourself after everything we covered here is why should I be choosing Get Movers? Here are only the few reasons why:
1.	All our movers are professionals and  exceptionally well trained.
2.	We use the latest technology solution to monitor live the process of your move, we know where our trucks are, crews located and their live actions (use Samsara) so while calling our customer service team will be able to answer all your questions live!
3.	Full customer service, support and management team is here to serve you 7 days a week!
4.	Back up trucks and crews in cases for last minute moves or emergencies 
5.	Exceptionally high referral rate based on our past customers that are referring us.
6.	Honest upfront pricing without any hidden fees or surprises after
7.	We are One stop shop for all your moving needs.
8.	Nationwide Canadian coverage allowing us serving you anywhere in Canada and US.
9.	Great Team with Over 12 years of successful experience in the moving industry.



So, call us now at 1888 to get your move arranged or Get your free quote on get movers.ca

Get Movers – Caring while Carrying

profile:
When we say that we move The Spirit of Your Home, we are not just using nice words, but real facts. Our company has always a complex approach to what moving means. We understand that our customers want us not to just move some stuff from one place to another, and we know that we are not just simply moving some furniture and stuffed boxes with things, but first of all, we are moving belongings with a deep spiritual value and memories for our customers. That is why it is extremely important for us to make sure that your things get safely to their destination and continue to provide your home with priceless memories.
Our priority is to make sure that all the possessions of our clients, which are filled with spiritual significance will bring the same joy throughout time, no matter how many times they are being moved to new houses, and our basic goal is to make sure that our clients remember us only from positive experience and perspective.

profile:
At TouchWood Movers, our mission is to make sure we are able to alleviate the moving stress off of the customer by providing top quality service without burning a hole in their pocket. We try to touch hearts with our craft, dedication and congeniality. 

WHY CHOOSE US:
 We always give written estimates whether it’s a flat price or an hourly price. All our in-house estimates are free of cost.
 We do not bring out hidden charges at the time of final payment.
 We charge reasonable prices and provide top notch service.
 All of our trucks are in mint condition and they carry all types of moving equipment.
 We are fully insured and bonded.
 We believe in growing and nurturing customer relationship.
 Last minute, short notice or advance bookings, we cater all.
 Our staff is extremely professional with an experience of more than 10 years. They know what they’re doing.

COVID UPDATE:
 We're doing our best to ensure the safety of our clients as well as our front-line crew members during this tough time:
 Our trucks are washed and sanitized periodically.
 All personal protective equipment including gloves and masks is mandatory for every crew member.
 As for the safety of our clients and crew members, we ask all our clients to avoid more than 2 people while moving and to maintain 2 m distance.

profile:
Quality service at an affordable price.

We're VR MOVING, a local, family-owned and operated professional moving service in Mississauga. Our local movers can handle moves of any size, including apartments, condos, single-family homes, retirement communities, dorms and more. VR MOVING is also specialized in moving any size of pianos, safes. When you move with us, you know your things will be safe. Before we move anything, our professional movers will protect your furniture with our heavy duty storage blankets. We also carry shrink wrap if your items need an extra layer of protection. To prevent any damage to large furniture items, we use shoulder harness straps and padded dollies. We also make sure we protect all your hardwood and tile floors when we get to your home. 
When you choose VR Moving, you know you’ll always get:
Upfront rates, with no hidden fees
On-time service
Friendly, uniformed movers
Fully licensed, insured, & honest service
When you arrange for a move with us, we’ll take care of everything. From showing up on time to keeping your costs as low as possible, you can feel confident that your project is in good hands. 
With over five  years of experience, in 2021 we started VR MOVING INC. While moving can be very stressful and can’t be cheap, the last thing people need is the unfair & over priced cost of a “professional” moving services. We believe there is a way to provide valuable, honest and professional moving services at an affordable prices. We're very excited to serve our community and we are committed to provide honest services.

profile:
IMPORTANT TO KNOW
- We always provide  written estimates that can be completed either in your home or over the phone, whichever is best for you. All estimates are free of cost.
- We do not surprise you with hidden charges at the time of final payment.
- We provide top notch service at reasonable prices

Why Should you feel comfortable in selecting us?
The processes we follow ensure you will receive a consistent result designed to exceed your expectations, reduce your stress levels and deliver you a happy comfortable experience.
Through our services we provide you tailor made solutions based on your needs, not out of the box offered to everyone.
We are local and family run, readily available to help you.
Our people are trained in a way that ensures you feel secure knowing your belongings are treated like they are our own.

QUESTIONS YOU SHOULD ASK EVERY COMPANY
1) Who Are You?
- We are a locally owned and operated family run business based in Mississauga, Ontario.   We are not your typical moving, storage or junk removal company.  We are a unique “One Stop ” solution for home owners and businesses.   We created Space Makers to help our clients run their lives and businesses with less stress and more comfort through less clutter.
We are “The simple solution to your Home’s (or businesses) evolution”

2) What Services Do You Offer?
- We offer the following:
Local moving – we pad, wrap and protect your belongings like they were our own.
Storage – we will remove and store items you do not need right now but may need in the future.
Junk – we will remove items you no longer need.
Donation or Auction – we will remove items you no longer need but do not want to see go to waste.
In home moving – for staging or simply rearranging, let us do the heavy lifting for you

3) What Do You Believe and why do you do what you do?
- We believe that no two client situations are the same.
- We believe that clients desire a “one stop” solution for their space making needs rather than dealing with numerous different service -providers.
- We believe that by properly analyzing the needs of our clients through client friendly conversation we will accurately understand their specific objectives.
- We believe that our clients deserve customized solutions with transparent quotes based on their specific objectives.
- We believe that by delivering quality and on-going training for all of our employees we will be an employer of choice for professional and personable employees.
- We believe that by having well-trained, professional and personable employees deliver a customized solution based on our understanding of our client’s objectives, we will be the “gold standard” for residential and commercial moving and storage.

4) Who do you work with?
- Our clients are just like you. We work with residential home-owners and renters to assist them with their local moves and with space-creation needs within their homes. 
- We also work with Business clients helping them with their moving and storage requirements.

5) What makes you different?
A) Our company
- Unique, not your average moving, storage or junk removal company.
- Local
- the simple solution to your home or business’s evolution.

B) Our Solutions
- Unique – tailored to your needs.
- Diverse, one stop company to reduce stress, save you time and money.
- Consistent, reliable, we follow our processes in every step.

C) Our People
- Well trained, professional and personable.
- Family run. We treat you and our team like they are our family - they are!
- Integrity, we were founded based on our core business beliefs including transparency and honesty.
